@node "gr1" "Ants"

@{fg shine} Ants games compilation@{fg text}

 Ants is a games compilation from Underground P.D, it contains 3 games; 
Ants, Bang!, and Skiddy Things.

 To start with, Ants is a cross between Worms & Lemmings, you are a
little guy who has to destroy a certain amount of ants to complete the 
level and gain a level code. It is very playable, and you can either
drop a bomb or blast the ants to kill them. The backdrops look like they
were created using a Voxel engine, like Scenery Creator, this makes the
graphics look unprofessional, but what do you expect from a P.D disk?

 Next up, is Bang!, this is a simple Bat `n' Ball game, but this one is 
mega, it has loads of bonuses, special features, and if you lose the
ball on any level it bounces back to the previous level until you catch 
it or it goes past level 1. Great!

 Last, is, what you could call a racing game, called Skiddy Things, you
are a little character who races against another character on one of 
four skiddy tracks. And, as a bonus, on the title screen you can play a
game of tennis!

